<subSubSection id="F444D993C07835D54EA5BB105569B2A7" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" type="notes">
<paragraph id="A57B29F1E0A687FE9A3AB63B3895BDD4" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph id="72FE346EA3C1A4A6186FB05D90F9E204" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">
Eleven new species were described (
<bibRefCitation id="02D10895A9EE905C73E77648A0808928" author="Han, Hongxiang" journalOrPublisher="Entomological Science" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="382 - 410" refId="B5535919" refString="Han, Hongxiang, Xue, Dayong, 2009. Taxonomic review of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China, with descriptions of seven new species (Lepidoptera: Geometridae, Geometrinae). Entomological Science 12 (4): 382 - 410" title="Taxonomic review of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China, with descriptions of seven new species (Lepidoptera: Geometridae, Geometrinae)" volume="12" year="2009">Han and Xue 2009</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="51A0D95869BF1B1294D9C1D4676C2829" author="Chang, W-C" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="538 - 550" refId="B5535782" refString="Chang, W-C, Wu, S, 2013. Review of the genus Hemistola Warren, 1893 in Taiwan with notes on an unusual conifer-feeding larva and descriptions of three new species (Lepidoptera, Geometridae, Geometrinae). Zootaxa 3741 (4): 538 - 550" title="Review of the genus Hemistola Warren, 1893 in Taiwan with notes on an unusual conifer-feeding larva and descriptions of three new species (Lepidoptera, Geometridae, Geometrinae)" volume="3741" year="2013">Chang and Wu 2013</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="943698A5CF6A9BA80D05E1FE1A2850A0" author="Wu, S" journalOrPublisher="Tinea" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="6 - 9" refId="B5537268" refString="Wu, S, 2019. Description of a new species of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China (Geometridae: Geometrinae). Tinea 25: 6 - 9" title="Description of a new species of Hemistola Warren, 1893 from China (Geometridae: Geometrinae)." volume="25" year="2019">Wu 2019</bibRefCitation>
). The species 
<taxonomicName id="38C57D5CC7F31126784BB2D208B6B9D7" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Hemistola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemistola flavitincta" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="flavitincta">
<emphasis id="0036BE367451743F9F399AB8CEB08C97" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Hemistola flavitincta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="ADD16532BC6932C86FE738ACAFA46F03" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Hemistola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemistola liliana" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="liliana">
<emphasis id="0A2707B0E91014C5AB87BF427AF01CC3" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Hemistola liliana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="5737AE1F11F0B8CCBAE8FF23C54CC624" authorityName="Swinhoe" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Herochroma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Herochroma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A37DADA33C9D82776E757CF472401046" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Herochroma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Swinhoe, 1893 by 
<bibRefCitation id="0A96EEDAB233915D263D49D0C76BFA5A" author="Parsons, MS" journalOrPublisher="CSIRO, Clayton North, Victoria, Australia" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" refId="B5536979" refString="Parsons, MS, Scoble, MJ, Honey, MR, Pitkin, LM, Pitkin, BR, 1999. Geometrid moths of the world: a catalogue (Lepidoptera, Geometridae). CSIRO, Clayton North, Victoria, Australia" title="Geometrid moths of the world: a catalogue (Lepidoptera, Geometridae)." year="1999">Parsons et al. (1999)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="94AFF6D3E3DEC43E54B7BC867D17571E" author="Pitkin, L" journalOrPublisher="Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" pagination="343 - 412" refId="B5536999" refString="Pitkin, L, Han, H, James, S, 2007. Moths of the tribe Pseudoterpnini (Geometridae: Geometrinae): a review of the genera. Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society 150 (2): 343 - 412" title="Moths of the tribe Pseudoterpnini (Geometridae: Geometrinae): a review of the genera" volume="150" year="2007">Pitkin et al. (2007)</bibRefCitation>
implied this was an editorial error and, citing a complete absence of 
<taxonomicName id="D4345C095FB4057124622DF85EEAE7CB" authorityName="Swinhoe" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Herochroma" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Herochroma" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="97DE20A340961CA505AF34E652C6DF9B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Herochroma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
diagnostic characters, transferred both species back to 
<taxonomicName id="F046B5BF4C1E3BCBC5E4ACAD3AA91467" authorityName="Warren" authorityYear="1893" class="Insecta" family="Geometridae" genus="Hemistola" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hemistola" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="07BBDAC8EE0698897B6C59D96DF3B404" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="52190">Hemistola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
